#: ../../incident-intelligence/incident-intelligence-overview.rst:16
msgid ""
"Detectors within Splunk Observability Cloud monitor your systems. As an "
"Observability Cloud user, you can configure detectors at varying "
"thresholds to generate alerts when something unusual happens, such as a "
"bug or issue. When a detector meets a specified threshold, it generates "
"alerts. A single detector can generate multiple alerts, particularly when"
" several issues occur at once, or when an issue persists over time and "
"causes further problems downstream. The end result is a countless number "
"of generated alerts."
